Description: Port libmimedir to Debian 12 Bookworm
 Rebuild for Debian 12 Bookworm.
 Replace debhelper compat file with debhelper-compat (= 13) in Build-Depends.
 Remove autotools-dev build dependency (superseded by dh-autoreconf).
 Rewrite debian/rules to use dh sequencer with --with autoreconf.
 Update Standards-Version to 4.6.2.
 Update .install files to use multiarch paths (usr/lib/*/).
 Create debian/not-installed to exclude libmimedir.la.
 AC_PROG_LIBTOOL replaced with LT_INIT and AC_CONFIG_MACRO_DIRS([m4]) added
 directly in configure.in source (baked in, not as patch hunk).
